Metrics for Measuring Security Culture
Objectives
By the end of this lab, students will be able to:

Design and implement a security culture measurement framework
Collect and analyze security awareness metrics using Python
Create interactive visualizations with D3.js for culture data
Generate actionable insights from security behavior patterns
Build a web-based dashboard for monitoring security culture
Prerequisites
Basic Python programming skills
Understanding of HTML, CSS, and JavaScript
Familiarity with cybersecurity concepts
Basic SQL knowledge
Linux command line experience
Lab Environment
Al Nafi provides pre-configured Linux cloud machines. Click Start Lab to access your environment with all necessary tools installed.

Lab Overview
This lab focuses on measuring organizational security culture through data collection, analysis, and visualization. You'll build a complete monitoring system to track training effectiveness, phishing resilience, incident patterns, and overall security awareness.

